lyrics:
[verse]
Pepa had a brand new jacket, oh so fine
With pinstripes and buttons that truly shine
He strutted down the street, with a swagger so cool
Everyone around him thought, "Man, that's one cool fool

[chorus]
Swingin' with Pepa, in his shiny jacket
Swayin' to the rhythm, he's got the perfect knack
Tapping his feet, with a stylish snap
Pepa and his jacket, he's got the swingin' knack
